title: Farewell To Fearless
description:
Taylor Swift graced us all by rerecording Fearless (Taylor's Version) and before we can move on, we have to say farewell to this fun era! Amy, Ana, Nick and Lacey painstakingly choose their top 5 songs from this album.
And now that we all know that Taylor isn't releasing another rerecording until November, what will we do in the meantime? Don't worry! We have something spectacular planned!
What's your fav 5 from Fearless? And what are you excited to hear next?
